CAPI=2:

name: iobundle:py2hwsw:iob_eth:0.1
#license: MIT
description: "IObundle's ethernet core. Driver-compatible with the [ethmac](https://opencores.org/projects/ethmac) core, containing a similar Control/Status Register interface."

